reviewText: We will a lot of fun with this adding new moves to what we already do
Love the YouTube videos so I decided to buy the DVDs- great instruction, easy to follow, variety of swing dance moves from beginner to advanced.

Great instructional video! Easy to follow!

This is a very good set of dvd's that does well with teaching the basic moves.  I bought to help teach my girlfriend how to swing dance.  Some of the moves are slightly different than how I originally learned but still a fantastic set of dvd's and the teachers use the glove trick to help with the teaching.  Very much recommended
